        <p><strong>PowerBASIC</strong> is the brand of several commercial compilers by PowerBASIC Inc. that compile a dialect of the {'BASIC'|link_urls:'/l'} programming language.</p>
        <p>There are both {'DOS'|link_urls:'i'} and {'Windows'|link_urls:'i'} versions, and two kinds of the latter: Console and Windows.</p>
